{"tid":2383914,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陸南海「沙長城」包圍台太平島","createTime":"2021-01-28T08:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T08:34:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3946139f534f001c379addc7a714e69f7653f3e6","tid":2383914,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T08:30:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210128/GDJAEAUVCBH3JIVXLSA4X7WIEI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210128%2FGDJAEAUVCBH3JIVXLSA4X7WIEI%2F&d=LvSu6Mc%2FVB7R449T953cU2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=4d83fbd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210128%2FGDJAEAUVCBH3JIVXLSA4X7WIEI%2F&h=75f12887\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210128/GDJAEAUVCBH3JIVXLSA4X7WIEI/</a><br />\n<br />\n陸南海「沙長城」包圍台太平島<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eECGN7TjMkWQCnOlpScdDBHy-8s=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QYODLEXSPZEX7CDUGTEBXP2O4E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeECGN7TjMkWQCnOlpScdDBHy-8s%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQYODLEXSPZEX7CDUGTEBXP2O4E.jpg&h=b545d3a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■衞星圖片顯示中國在南海建立人工軍事島嶼基地。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n中國無視2016年海牙仲裁法庭的判決，近年在南海八個島礁建立軍事基地，更把台灣控制的太平島重重包圍。南海幾成為前美軍太平洋司令哈里斯所言的「沙長城（Great wall of sand）」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：指開放美豬含瘦肉精 藉口打擊經濟  陸搞分化 封殺台肉類產品<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可泊戰艦 供軍機升降<br />\n<br />\n據台灣《中時電子報》報道，陸方已軍事化八個島礁，其中一個位於西沙群島，其餘七個則位於南沙群島。大陸在南海現擁有四個高度軍事化基地，每個基地均有3,000米跑道及港口，可供軍機升降及軍艦停泊。<br />\n<br />\n大陸在南沙群島的七個軍事島礁，按戰略位置可分為外三角及內三角，外三角由渚碧礁、美濟礁和永暑礁三座有軍事機場及港口的島礁，包圍整個南沙群島。內三角則由南薰礁、東門礁、赤瓜礁有堡壘式軍事建築的島礁組成，專門監控鄭和群礁及九章群礁的各國駐軍，及台灣太平島一帶海域的異動。南方還有華陽礁作為堡壘島礁，監控越南軍事中心南威島。至於位於西沙、有機場及港口的永興島，則是解放軍自大陸通往南沙的重要中轉站。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：日趨勢大師：習希魔化勿姑息<br />\n<br />\n中國國務院去年已宣佈在西沙、南沙群島設置「西沙行政區」及「南沙行政區」，兩者政府分設西沙永興島及南沙永暑礁。<br />\n<br />\n《中時電子報》"},{"pid":"2404c9141086fe07b4322d227af7f26ff3e5e6c5","tid":2383914,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T08:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b349054563daef4d28d782cd72fb18e3fc969beb","tid":2383914,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T08:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/02db87/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/d/attachments/day_191118/20191118_7aec43fef299266fe6f1KUS61hkM4nfL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F02db87%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.discuss.com.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_191118%2F20191118_7aec43fef299266fe6f1KUS61hkM4nfL.jpg&h=f6c4de0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ff2fb8c806dfb44a689b4a7fdffd53052e83767","tid":2383914,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T08:34:24.000Z","msg":"老蕭講呢單嘢<br />\n<br />\n蕭若元 北京心急喊話美國！？ 拜登政府強調戰略耐心！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2383918\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2383918</a>"}],"pinned":{"pid":"7ff2fb8c806dfb44a689b4a7fdffd53052e83767","tid":2383914,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T08:34:24.000Z","msg":"老蕭講呢單嘢<br />\n<br />\n蕭若元 北京心急喊話美國！？ 拜登政府強調戰略耐心！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2383918\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2383918</a>"}}